== Conviction ==
On 11 August 2024, a car accident caused by Aboul Fotouh on the [[Cairo–Alexandria desert road|Cairo-Alexandria road]] led to the death of a 55-year-old man. Aboul Fotouh was accompanied by his teammate, goalkeeper [[Mohamed Sobhy (footballer, born 1999)|Mohamed Sobhy]]. The examination proved that Aboul Fotouh was under the influence of drugs. He was detained for 4 days pending investigation. On 13 August, his detention was renewed for 15 days.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-08-13 |title=تجديد حبس أحمد فتوح 15 يوما فى واقعة دهس أمين شرطة على طريق الساحل |url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2024/8/13/%D8%AA%D8%AC%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%AF-%D8%AD%D8%A8%D8%B3-%D8%A3%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF-%D9%81%D8%AA%D9%88%D8%AD-15-%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85%D8%A7-%D9%81%D9%89-%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%82%D8%B9%D8%A9-%D8%AF%D9%87%D8%B3-%D8%A3%D9%85%D9%8A%D9%86/6672929 |access-date=2024-08-25 |website=اليوم السابع |language=ar}}</ref> He first appeared in court on 19 August. The case was adjourned until 16 September and he will remain in prison.<ref>{{Cite web |title=لاعب الزمالك من قفص الاتهام :"لا أتعاطى المخدرات" |url=https://www.alarabiya.net/arab-and-world/egypt/2024/08/19/%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B2%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83-%D9%85%D9%86-%D9%82%D9%81%D8%B5-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%85-%D9%84%D8%A7-%D8%A3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%B7%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%AE%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA- |access-date=August 25, 2024 |website=www.alarabiya.net}}</ref> On 16 September, Abou El Fotouh was released on a 50,000 Egyptian pound bail, with the case scheduled for review on 22 October.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.skynewsarabia.com/sport/1742122-%D9%85%D8%B5%D8%B1-%D9%82%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%AD%D9%83%D9%85%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%B6%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%94%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF-%D9%81%D8%AA%D9%88%D8%AD |title=مصر.. قرار من المحكمة في قضية أحمد فتوح |publisher=Sky News Arabia |language=ar |date=16 September 2024 }}</ref> The [[Matrouh Governorate|Matrouh]] Criminal Court decided to postpone the trial of Aboul Fotouh to the November 16 session for pleading. Members of the victim's family attended, acknowledging the reconciliation.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2024/10/22/%D8%AA%D8%A3%D8%AC%D9%8A%D9%84-%D9%85%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%83%D9%85%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF-%D9%81%D8%AA%D9%88%D8%AD-%D9%84%D8%AC%D9%84%D8%B3%D8%A9-16-%D9%86%D9%88%D9%81%D9%85%D8%A8%D8%B1-%D9%84%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B9%D8%A9/6750571 |title=تأجيل محاكمة أحمد فتوح لجلسة 16 نوفمبر للمرافعة |publisher=youm7.com |language=ar |date=22 October 2024 }}</ref>

On 16 November 2024, the Matrouh Criminal Court sentenced Aboul Fotouh to one year in prison, suspended for three years, along with a fine of 20,000 EGP, and revoked his driver's license. A written agreement was also made between the player and the victim's family, in which Aboul Fotouh committed to paying a 10 million EGP [[Blood money (restitution)|blood money]] to the family. The agreement also stipulated that the family would not pursue any further legal claims against him.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.alarabiya.net/arab-and-world/egypt/2024/11/16/سنة-مع-ايقاف-التنفيذ-الحكم-على-لاعب-الزمالك-أحمد-فتوح |title=سنة مع إيقاف التنفيذ.. الحكم على لاعب الزمالك أحمد فتوح |publisher=Al Arabiya |language=ar |date=16 November 2024 }}</ref> On 9 February 2025, the court rejected Aboul Fotouh's appeal against his sentence, maintaining the original ruling, despite efforts by his defense team to challenge the decision.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2025/2/9/رفض-استئناف-أحمد-فتوح-لاعب-الزمالك-على-حكم-حبسه-سنة/6877746 |title=رفض استئناف أحمد فتوح لاعب الزمالك على حكم حبسه سنة مع إيقاف التنفيذ |publisher=youm7.com |language=ar |date=9 February 2025 }}</ref>

